snippet.title: Ninja Kidz Time Masters - Official Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10007611

Ready to become a ninja? Become one with the official game of Ninja Kidz. America's most popular online ninja family's first video game is here! A colourful action adventure for the whole family where you can play alone or together with friends. Rescue the 3 greatest martial arts masters kidnapped by Dr. Disaster.

#ps5 #ps5games #ps4 #ps4games
